<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Doctor - Surgenesis Hospital</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style1.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f3f7fb;
      color: #003865;
    }

    .doctor-container {
      display: flex;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .doctor-card {
      flex: 2;
      margin-right: 30px;
    }

    .doctor-info {
      margin-left: 24px;
    }

    .doctor-info h1 {
      color: #BD1E1E;
      font-size: 22px;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }

    .doctor-info h2 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin: 4px 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .appointment-section {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .booknow {
      background-color: #BD1E1E;
      color: #ffffff;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .popup {
      display: none;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .form-text {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
    }

    .form-text[type="submit"] {
      background-color: #003865;
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
    }

    .form-text[type="submit"]:hover {
      background-color: #BD1E1E;
    }

    .about-section {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .about-section h2 {
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #003865;
    }

    .about-section a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .about-section p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include("partial/header") %>

  <div class="doctor-container">
    <div class="doctor-card">
      <div class="img-text" style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start;">
        <img class="img-dd" src="/images/dd1.jpg" alt="Dr. Vivek Mittal">
        <div class="doctor-info" >
          <div style="line-height: 28px;"><h1>Dr. Amit Mittal</h1>
          <h2 style="display:flex;flex:inline-left;">Senior Consultant</h2>
          <h2 style="display:flex;flex:inline-left;"><strong>Department:</strong><p style="display: flex;flex-direction:row;margin:0px;padding-left:2px">MBBS, DNB, FNB</p></h2>
          <h2 style="display:flex;flex:inline-left;"><strong>Experience:</strong> 22 Years</h2></div>
          <div class="dr-btn"><p style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom:6px"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone" style="color:#BD1E1E; margin-right: 10px;"></i><strong>For Appointment</strong></p><p style="padding-left: 5px;padding-top:5px;">9079888679</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>About Dr. <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=dr.+amit+mittal+on+google" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent;">Amit Mittal</a></h2>
        <p>Dr. Amit Mittal is an orthopedic and hand surgeon practicing in Jaipur, Rajasthan. He is known for his <strong>expertise</strong> in hand and <strong>microsurgery</strong>, including treatment of brachial plexus injuries, congenital anomalies, and spastic hand management. He is associated with <strong>Surgenesis Hospital</strong> and Mittal Hand Microsurgery Centre in Jaipur.</p>
        <p>He has managed major degloving injuries of upper and lower limb including pediatric patient successfully. He got <strong>2nd rank in Diplomat National</strong> board in Hand and Microsurgery-2012 [DNB-FNB].</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="appointment-section">
      <button onclick="togglePopup3()" class="booknow"><a href="/contact" style="background-color: transparent;color:white; text-decoration:none">Book an Appointment <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right" style="margin-left: 10px;"></i></a></button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include("partial/footer") %>

  <script>
    function togglePopup3() {
      const popup = document.getElementById('popupForm');
      popup.style.display = (popup.style.display === 'block') ? 'none' : 'block';
    }
  </script>
  <script>
  function toggleMobileNav() {
    const panel = document.getElementById('mobileNav');
    panel.classList.toggle('active');
  }

  function toggleDropdown(trigger) {
    trigger.parentElement.classList.toggle('active');
  }
</script>

</body>

</html>






